datalog_relationships:
is_conflicted(S) :- pc_member(S), subject_attribute(S, 'isConflicted', 'true').
is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid(S) :- pc_member(S), subject_attribute(S, 'isEq-subjUserId-resUserId', 'true').
subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), subject_attribute(S, 'subjReviewsThisResPaper', 'true'), resource_attribute(R, 'paper', 'true').
has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), subject_attribute(S, 'hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper', 'true'), resource_attribute(R, 'paper', 'true').
phase_discussion(R) :- resource(R), resource_attribute(R, 'phase', 'discussion').
is_see_unassigned_allowed(R) :- resource(R), resource_attribute(R, 'isSeeUnassignedAllowed', 'true').
datalog_actions:
can_read(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), subject_attribute(S, 'role', 'pc-member'), subject_attribute(S, 'isConflicted', 'false'), action(S, 'read'), (is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid(S); phase_discussion(R); (subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, R), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, R)); is_see_unassigned_allowed(R)), not denied(S, R).
denied(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), not (is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid(S); phase_discussion(R); (subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, R), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, R)); is_see_unassigned_allowed(R)).
can_delete(S) :- Subject(S), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_read(S, R) :- pc_member(S), meeting_paper(R), action(S, "read").
can_create(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "pc-member").
can_access(U, R, 'read') :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, 'admin'). can_access(U, R, 'write') :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, 'admin').
can_access(S, R, 'read') :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_access(S, R, 'read') :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'pc-member'), has_isMeeting(S, 'true').
carminati: Subject(?S) ∧ Resource(?R) ∧ role(?S,"pc-chair") ∧ isSubjectsMeeting(?S,"true") ∧ ?isEq-meet in ?gPaper-resId(R, "true") => can_access(?S,?R,"read")

can_access(U, R, "create") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "pc-member"), is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(U, "true").
can_access(U, R, "delete") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "pc-member"), is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(U, "true").

carminati: Subject(?S) ∧ Resource(?R) ∧ has_role(?S,"pc-member") ∧ is_conflicted(?S,"false") ∧ is_eq_subj_user_id_res_user_id(?S,?"true"). can_read(S,?R) => can_read(?S,?R)

has_subjReviewsThisResPaper(S, "true") :- AccessSubject(S).
has_hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper(S, "true") :- AccessSubject(S).

has_isSeeUnassignedAllowed(R, "true") :- Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_read(S, R) :- AccessSubject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), has_isConflicted(S, "false"), (has_isEq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true") ; has_phase(R, "discussion") ; (has_subjReviewsThisResPaper(S, "true"), has_hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper(S, "true")) ; has_isSeeUnassignedAllowed(R, "true")).
can_delete(U, Res) :- User(U), Resource(Res), has_role(U, 'pc-chair').
can_read(S, MP) :- PC_Member(S), MeetingPaper(MP), isEq_meetingPaper(MP).
can_create(S, O) :- pc_member(S), object(O).
can_access(U, Res, Action) :- User(U), Resource(Res), role(U, "admin"), (Action = "read"; Action = "write").
carminati: Subject(?S) ∧ Resource(?R) ∧ role(?S,"pc-chair") ∧ isSubjectsMeeting(?S,"true") ∧ isEq_meetingPaper_resId(?R,"true") => can_access(?S,?R,"read")

datalog_actions: can_access(S, O, 'read') :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_read(S, M) :- pc_member(S), meeting(M), is_meeting(S).

carminati: Subject(?S) ∧ Resource(?R) ∧ has_role(?S,'pc-member') ∧ is_conflicted(?S,?false) ∧ (is_eq_subj_user_id_res_user_id(?S,?true) ; phase(?R,'discussion') ; (subj_reviews_this_res_paper(?S,?true), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S,?true)) ; is_see_unassigned_allowed(?R,?true)) => can_read(?S,?R)

can_access(U, P) :- User(U), Paper(P), has_role(U, 'pc-chair'), not_conflicted(U).

can_create(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "subreviewer"), is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true").
can_access(S) :- has_role(S, "pc-chair"), not_conflicted(S).

has_role(S, "pc-member") :- Subject(S).
is_conflicted(S, "false") :- Subject(S).
is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
phase(R, "discussion") :- Resource(R).
is_see_unassigned_allowed(R, "true") :- Resource(R).
datalog_actions:
can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), is_conflicted(S, "false"), is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true").
can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), is_conflicted(S, "false"), phase(R, "discussion").
can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), is_conflicted(S, "false"), subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, "true"), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, "true").
can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), is_conflicted(S, "false"), is_see_unassigned_allowed(R, "true").
not can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), is_conflicted(S, "false"), not (is_eq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true"); phase(R, "discussion"); (subj_reviews_this_res_paper(S, "true"), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper(S, "true")); is_see_unassigned_allowed(R, "true")).
can_delete(U, Res) :- User(U), Resource(Res), has_role(U, "pc-chair").
can_read(S, MP) :- PC_Member(S), MeetingPaper(MP), isEq_meetingPaper_resId(MP, "true").
can_create(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "pc-member").

can_access(U, R, "read") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin").
can_access(U, R, "write") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "admin").
can_access(S, R, 'read') :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_access(S, R, "read") :- AccessSubject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), has_isMeeting(S, "true").
can_access(S, R, Action) :- PCMember(S), Resource(R), is_same_user(S, R), member(Action, [write, create, delete]).

is_same_user(U, R) :- User(U), Resource(R).
datalog_actions:
can_access(U, R, "write") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "pc-member"), is_same_user(U, R).
can_access(U, R, "create") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "pc-member"), is_same_user(U, R).
can_access(U, R, "delete") :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "pc-member"), is_same_user(U, R).

datalog_relationships:
has_role(U, "subreviewer") :- User(U).
is_same_user(U, R) :- User(U), Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_create(U, R) :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, "subreviewer"), is_same_user(U, R).
can_access(U, P) :- User(U), Paper(P), has_role(U, "pc-chair"), has_conflict_status(U, "false").

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, "pc-chair") :- Subject(S).
is_subjects_meeting(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
is_eq_meeting_paper_res_id(R, "true") :- Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-chair"), is_subjects_meeting(S, "true"), is_eq_meeting_paper_res_id(R, "true").

can_access(U, create, Res) :- User(U), Resource(Res), has_role(U, pc-chair).
can_access(U, delete, Res) :- User(U), Resource(Res), has_role(U, pc-chair).
deny_access(S) :- Subject(S), is_conflicted(S).

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, "pc-member") :- Subject(S).
has_isConflicted(S, "false") :- Subject(S).
has_isEq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
has_subjReviewsThisResPaper(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
has_hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper(S, "true") :- Subject(S).
has_phase(R, "discussion") :- Resource(R).
has_isSeeUnassignedAllowed(R, "true") :- Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_read(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, "pc-member"), has_isConflicted(S, "false"), (has_isEq_subjUserId_resUserId(S, "true"); has_phase(R, "discussion"); (has_subjReviewsThisResPaper(S, "true"), has_hasSubmittedReviewForResPaper(S, "true")); has_isSeeUnassignedAllowed(R, "true")).
can_delete(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_read(S, P) :- pc_member(S), meeting_paper(P).
can_create(S, R) :- PCMember(S), Resource(R).
can_access(S, "read") :- Subject(S). can_access(S, "write") :- Subject(S).
can_access(S, 'read') :- Subject(S), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_read(S, M) :- PC_Member(S), Meeting(M), is_in_meeting(S).
deny_all :- false.
can_access(S) :- PCChair(S).
can_access(U) :- User(U), has_role(U, 'pc-chair'), not_conflicted(U).

datalog_relationships:
is_conflicted_false(S) :- pc_member(S).
is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid_true(S) :- pc_member(S).
subj_reviews_this_res_paper_true(S) :- pc_member(S).
has_submitted_review_for_res_paper_true(S) :- pc_member(S).
phase_discussion(R) :- resource(R).
is_see_unassigned_allowed_true(R) :- resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_read(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R), is_conflicted_false(S), (is_eq_subjuserid_resuserid_true(S); phase_discussion(R); (subj_reviews_this_res_paper_true(S), has_submitted_review_for_res_paper_true(S)); is_see_unassigned_allowed_true(R)).
can_delete(U, Res) :- User(U), Resource(Res), has_role(U, 'pc-chair').
can_read(S, P) :- pc_member(S), meeting_paper(P).
can_create(S) :- Subject(S), has_role(S, 'pc-member').
can_access(U, R, read) :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, 'admin'). can_access(U, R, write) :- User(U), Resource(R), has_role(U, 'admin').
can_access(S, R, 'read') :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'pc-chair').
can_read(P, M) :- PCMember(P), Meeting(M), is_in_meeting(P, M).

can_access(S, read) :- Subject(S), role(S, pc-chair).
can_access(S, write) :- Subject(S), role(S, pc-chair).
can_access(S, O, "read") :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "pc-member").
can_access(S, O, 'read') :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, 'admin'). can_access(S, O, 'write') :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, 'admin').
can_access(U, Res, read) :- User(U), Resource(Res), has_role(U, pc-chair).
can_read(P, M) :- PCMember(P), Meeting(M), is_meeting(P).
